      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.Dysu4F8licjEb2FY]{Vanguard Discipline}</p>\n<p>You can use entropy to bolster your stance when wielding a shield. As a reaction while wielding a shield, you can spend 1 Entropy Point to gain a +4 circumstance bonus to your AC or a saving throw against any effect that would move you, such as @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.U37n5tY5hn1ctzQL.JournalEntryPage.R33uiOMesYP0ISWl#bull-rush]{Bull Rush}, @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.U37n5tY5hn1ctzQL.JournalEntryPage.R33uiOMesYP0ISWl#reposition]{Reposition}, and @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.U37n5tY5hn1ctzQL.JournalEntryPage.R33uiOMesYP0ISWl#trip]{Trip }combat maneuvers.</p>\n<p><em>Select and enable the appropriate bonus in the Modifiers tab.</em></p>"
